## Configuration
To run this app locally, first create a python virtual environment using <br>
`python3.11 -m venv venv`

Then enter the virtual environment <br>
`venv\Scripts\activate`

Install the dependencies in the virtual environment <br>
`pip install -r requirements.txt`

Create a environment variables file called `.env` including the following information:
```
OPENAI_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_SA_JSON_PATH=  // This should be the path to youre google cloud json credentials
SHEET_ID=
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5-nano
```

Run the app using <br>
`streamlit run app.py`

To deactivate the virtual environment <br>
`venv\Scripts\deactivate.bat`

## Docker
To build a docker container of the project run <br>
`docker build -t smart-followup .`

Run the container using <br>
`docker run -p 8501:8501 --env-file .env smart-followup`
